author: dlr
msg: On the merge-tracking branch: Avoid discarding any additional merge
info which entered the WC as the result of a property merge.
* subversion/libsvn_client/diff.c
(do_merge, do_single_file_merge): Re-parse the merge info reflected
by the WC before using it to update its merge info based on the
revision ranges which were just merged in.
Patch by: dlr
madanus

author: rooneg
msg: Merge r20423 from trunk into the 1.4.x branch.
Re-order the arguments of svn_txdelta_to_svndiff2(), a new API in 1.4,
so that they meet our conventions of:
- output parameters come first
- pool comes last
